# SkillSphere Project Rules

## Code Style
- Use Black for code formatting
- Follow MyPy type checking rules
- Adhere to Ruff linting guidelines
- Maintain 100% test coverage

## Project Patterns
- FastAPI for API endpoints
- Neo4j for graph storage
- Node2Vec for embeddings
- Ollama for local AI processing

## Error Handling
- Consistent error messages
- Standard status codes
- Proper validation
- Clear error documentation

## Testing
- Unit tests for all components
- Integration tests for core flows
- Coverage reporting
- Error case coverage

## Documentation
- Keep Memory Bank updated
- Document API changes
- Update error patterns
- Maintain test documentation

## Development Workflow
- Use virtual environment
- Run tests before commits
- Check type hints
- Verify coverage

## Project Structure
- Follow module organization
- Maintain clear imports
- Use proper file naming
- Keep documentation current 